  "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds the complete **Dealix Startup Operating System** as an additive layer\nacross company strategy, product, website, commercial GTM, sales, marketing,\nmedia/social, ads planning, a 400+/day founder-review draft factory, CRM/RevOps,\ndelivery, support, finance, legal/compliance, security/trust, analytics, people,\npartnerships, investor readiness, operations, go-live, and final launch control.\n\nNo backend, web pages, or migrations were modified — this is purely additive.\n\n## Includes\n\n- **21 OS doc areas + 5 vertical playbooks** (bilingual AR/EN, 224 docs) under\n  `docs/*-os/`, `docs/site-launch/`, `docs/commercial-launch/`, `docs/go-live/`,\n  `docs/launch-control/`.\n- **400+/day Draft Factory** (`scripts/commercial_generate_400_drafts.py`):\n  175 cold email / 100 follow-up / 75 LinkedIn manual / 50 website form. Every\n  draft hard-flags `send_allowed=false`, `external_send_blocked=true`,\n  `requires_founder_approval=true`, `no_auto_send=true`.\n- **Founder Review Queue** + quality/compliance gates, scoring, metrics, seed\n  validation.\n- **Media/Social OS** 30-day calendar generator (planning only, no auto-post).\n- **CRM/RevOps schema** (`send_capability: none`), analytics taxonomy, ads seed\n  (not live).\n- **Verifier spine**: safety audit, launch readiness, site/api static checks,\n  CRM verify, scoped secret scan, `final_launch_control_verify.py`,\n  `startup_os_verify.py`.\n- **16 stdlib test suites** (35 tests).\n- **5 GitHub Actions** — `workflow_dispatch` + `schedule`,\n  `permissions: contents: read`, artifact-only, no secrets, no committed outputs.\n- README Startup OS section, Repository Discovery Report, Evidence Pack.\n\n## Safety\n\n- No external sending. No SMTP. No WhatsApp outbound. No LinkedIn automation.\n- No website form auto-submit. No scraping. No live paid ads. No secrets.\n- All drafts require founder approval; the system only drafts, scores, ranks,\n  analyzes, and recommends.\n- CI workflows are read-only / artifact-only.\n\n## Tests Run (real results)\n\n- `pytest` — 16 Startup OS suites → **35 passed**.\n- `startup_os_verify.py` → **PASS** (21 areas, 224 docs).\n- `final_launch_control_verify.py` → **PASS** (15/15 critical steps).\n- `commercial_safety_audit.py` → **PASS** (400 drafts, external_send blocked).\n- `final_secret_and_risk_scan.py --strict` → **PASS** (308 files, 0 secrets).\n- `make env-check` → **PASS**; `make api-contract-check` → **PASS**.\n- `apps/web` `npm run verify` (typecheck + Next build) → **PASS**.\n- `make security-smoke` → **pre-existing FAIL** in unrelated existing test\n  fixtures/docs (fake secrets), **not** introduced by this PR; the scoped Startup\n  OS scanner passes cleanly.\n\n## Final Go/No-Go\n\n- **GO**: public website (builds), commercial positioning, 400 review-only\n  drafts, founder manual review, media/social planning + manual posting, paid\n  diagnostics, discovery, proposals, pilot planning, analytics schema,\n  delivery/support prep, finance templates, legal templates pending legal review.\n- **NO-GO (permanently out of scope)**: automated email/WhatsApp/LinkedIn\n  sending, form auto-submit, bulk sending, live paid ads without\n  tracking/compliance, processing sensitive data before agreement, external\n  sending from CI, unproven claims.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01HD5qnGdRtc6AHAcTo2ByJq\n\n---\n_Generated by [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code/session_01HD5qnGdRtc6AHAcTo2ByJq)_",
